title: Lincoln Ave 2 Bedroom | Modern Kitchen/Bath |W/D | Garage | Yard
posting_body: ['If you are interested in this Two-Bedroom in Summit Hill request a tour so our friendly guest service team may help you.', 'Visit', 'stpaulrental com', 'and click', 'REQUEST A TOUR', '.', 'For everything else contact our friendly and welcoming guest service team for help with our top-tier homes in prime locations at', 'show contact info', 'or', 'help <at> stpaulrental com', 'Now accepting tour requests for the new two-bedroom on a quiet tree-lined cul-de-sac in the Summit Hill neighborhood of St Paul.', 'The home has many luxuries, including a modern kitchen and bathroom, dishwasher, new flooring, high ceilings, an open concept floor plan, 1.5 car garage, a fenced yard, a washer/dryer, and many windows to draw in plenty of natural sunlight and outdoor views.', 'Summit Hill is always full of interesting, celebrated people and you will entertain them in your luxurious dining room separated from the new kitchen by solid hardwood double-swing doors.', ' The Summit Hill neighborhood has excellent public spaces, and this home is within walking distance to epic Summit Avenue Exercise Trails and Bikeways, Universities, and Colleges.', 'There is always abundant and safe street parking just steps from your front door on the quiet residential cul-de-sac.', 'The School district is 625.', 'The security deposit is equal to one month’s rent.', 'Utilities, trash, taxes, and other costs vary based upon actual usage.', 'The lease is 12+ months.', 'This lovely home is available for immediate move-in with good credit.', 'Visit stpaulrental com and click REQUEST A TOUR when you’re ready to view this home on a quiet tree-lined cul-de-sac in the epic Summit Hill neighborhood of St Paul.', 'For everything else, contact our friendly guest service team for help finding a top-tier home in a prime location', 'show contact info', 'or help @ stpaulrental com']
